sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant Admin
participant Frontend
participant API
participant DB

Admin->>Frontend: View booking reports
Frontend->>API: GET /api/bookings/reports
API->>API: requireAuth
alt Not authenticated
API-->>Frontend: 401 Authentication is required
Frontend-->>Admin: Show auth error
else Authenticated
API->>API: Check is_admin
alt Not admin
API-->>Frontend: 403 Admin access is required
Frontend-->>Admin: Show forbidden
else Admin
API->>DB: Query summary stats
API->>DB: Query bookings by location
API->>DB: Query upcoming bookings
alt DB error
DB-->>API: error
API-->>Frontend: 500 with error message
Frontend-->>Admin: Show error state
else Success
DB-->>API: report rows
API-->>Frontend: 200 reports payload
Frontend-->>Admin: Render reports
end
end
end
